# Migration documentation workflow

After completing a migration batch (one or more related features/commands):

1. **changelog.md** (repo root) — add an `[Unreleased]` entry with what was ported and any breaking or notable behavior changes
2. **docs/ROADMAP.md** — check off completed items or update phase status for `buildx-server`
3. **docs/buildx-cli-migration.md** — update command parity table when CLI commands are ported
4. **docs/ARCHITECTURE.md** — update package mapping or naming deviations only when structure changes

Keep entries concise and dated when releasing versions. Link to OneDev/tod source paths under `references/` when helpful for traceability.
